HORRIBLE CUSTOMER SERVICE As my companions and I walk into the corner store of a building, we are smoldered with the heat of the attitude from the workers. We order our very over priced meal and wait for it in the designated waiting area, which so happens to be featured in the volcanic heat of a new orleans summer. After about 15 minutes of standing up and waiting outside to be serviced our food, we are delivered the wrong order with a side of attitude from the same worker. After we retrieve our food,  I go back to the jail cell of a  window to ask for a simple plate for my companion and I to share our meal. But instead, I was given an unpretentious sized plate. As I gently asked for another plate, I was then told no. What kind’ve of business tells the customer they can’t have a plain plate? After I paid for this overpriced food and dealt with your attitude, AND had my order messed up I know that I will NEVER be returning to this establishment again.
